## 7. Sponsors (layer, not node type)

Sponsors attach via **metadata**, not node type.

```jsonc
"sponsors": {
  "sponsor_001": {
    "id": "sponsor_001",
    "name": "Pika Cola",
    "logoId": "pika_cola_logo",
    "url": "https://pikacola.com",
    "metadata": {}
  }
}
```

Attachment model:

- **Global**: `hunt.settings.sponsorIds: ["sponsor_001"]`
- **Per-node**: `node.metadata.sponsorId: "sponsor_001"`

Runtime:

- Uses this to show overlays, logos, or link nodes—but **sponsors never become node types**.

