## 8. How this maps to your current UI

- **Admin dashboard / node editor**  
  - Edits `nodes[id]` objects (type, title, body, next, choices, requirements, effects, timer, failNodeId).
  - “State Effects (JSON)” in your UI → `onEnter.effects` / `onExit.effects`.
  - “Reward on Enter/Exit” → `onEnter.rewardId` / `onExit.rewardId`.
  - “Requires Items” → `requirements.items`.
  - “Fail Node ID” → `failNodeId`.

- **Items screen**  
  - Edits `items[id]`.

- **Rewards screen**  
  - Edits `rewards[id]`.

- **Gameplay screen**  
  - Reads from `nodes`, `items`, `rewards`, `settings`.
  - Uses runtime state + this schema to render everything.

